Report message as spam

Usage: mxr spam [OPTIONS] [MESSAGE_ID]...

Arguments:
  [MESSAGE_ID]...

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>
      --yes
      --dry-run
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
